ygData.messageBody:
I just recently ventured down to Upper Guk to get my armor quest item, and I
must say that UGuk very viable for a 20s group. There are NO crowds and the
frogs are plentiful. I would suggest bringing a tank with you and/or a
healer type and you're all set.

Utendar of Veeshan
